  "description": "Now that I have started developing my files, it is easy to get overwhelmed by the many directions I can go. An idea I\u0026rsquo;ve just had is that it would be good for me to be able to put a disclaimer before certain types of text, for example making sure that babbles disclose that they\u0026rsquo;re, well, babble-y, or that any essay that\u0026rsquo;s more than a couple years old has a good chance of being wrong.\n",
